title: You need help editing you little bitch?
description: These cmds create and edit embedded messages.

fields.name: corn?add [attribute] [value]
fields.value:
Adds/updates the specified attribute with a specific value to the currernt message.
Use corn?help attributes for a list of all attributes.
Ex: corn?add title Christianity and its Consequences

fields.name: corn?remove [attribute]
fields.value:
Removes the specified attribute from the current message.
Ex: corn?remove footer-text
